name: Mina Protocol (httpz) 🪶
fullText:
1/ 🚀 A step toward fully automating hard forks & protocol upgrades for Mina.

With this change, nodes will pre-migrate ledgers in the background during normal operation. When the fork hits, they’ll already have everything ready to switch instantly and autonomously. https://t.co/nv42CKkZCz

name: pseudo 🇺🇦
fullText:
the secret to growth in all aspects of life:

embrace being awkward.

tweet your thoughts (even if you find it cringe)
speak that new language poorly
write some stupid essays

the fear of being seen as awkward is what separates average people from great people
